  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You throw a handful of sand that transforms into jagged shards of glass. Creatures in the area take 4d6 slashing damage and must attempt a Reflex save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target takes half damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The target takes full damage and @Damage[1[bleed]]{1 persistent bleed} damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target takes double damage and 2 persistent bleed damage.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The damage increases by 2d6.</p>"
